  "title": "CONSTRUCTION MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>· Assist in planning and creating schedules and project timelines.</p><p>· Overseeing and directing construction works from conception to completion</p><p>· Coordinate and direct workers and subcontractors</p><p>· Ensure quality construction standards and the use of proper construction techniques</p><p>· Track deliverables, control subcontractors and suppliers to meet schedule, safety and quality objectives.</p><p>· Planning of housekeeping by coordinating responsibilities of site engineers / site supervisors and sub-contractors.</p><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><p>· Recognized Degree in Civil Engineering, with a minimum of 5 years experience in the Construction industry locally.</p><p>· Strong leadership and supervisory skills</p><p>· A team player with good communication skills</p><p>· Meticulous and attentive to details</p><p>· Excellent communication skills, both written and verbal</p>",
